        "name": "Normalized hemolysis index prediction within 15% of experimental mean",
        "description": "The CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) must fall within 15% of the experimental ensemble mean across all five operating points."
      },
      "rationale": "CFD NIH predictions ranged from 8% below to 12% above experimental means across the five operating points. All points satisfy the 15% criterion. Level 3 achieved."
    },
    {
